  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `v1.8.14-unstable-eef65b20/linux-amd64/go1.10.3`\r\nOS & Version: Debian 8\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nReceipt event fires once the transaction got mined\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nEvent fires on every new block\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nSend transaction with \r\n\r\n````\r\nweb3.eth.sendTransaction({\r\n  from: ownerAddress,\r\n  to: address,\r\n  value:sendAmount,\r\n   gas: gas\r\n})\r\n.on('transactionHash', function(hash){\r\n //FIRES ONCE AS SUPPOSED TO                            \r\n})\r\n.on('receipt', function(receipt){\r\n  //FIRES ON EVERY BLOCK UNTIL RESTART\r\n})",
